title: The Danger Of Dry Places | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: The Danger Of Dry Places | Joel Osteen
description:
You may be in a dry season, but you have to remember it's not permanent. It's just a matter of time before you see your breakthrough!

 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
